---
// Section 3 — The "what I'm building toward" section (v2)
// Integrated into site theme — no dark bg, 55vh, centered
---

<section class="relative z-10 flex items-center border-b border-border/50 bg-bg" style="min-height: 55vh;">
  <div class="section-shell w-full">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">

      {/* Label */}
      <div class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-border" />
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-muted-foreground uppercase">
          Direction
        </span>
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-border" />
      </div>

      {/* Main statement */}
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-light text-foreground md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl" style="line-height: 1.25;">
        Building at the intersection of
        <span class="font-medium italic"> design</span> and
        <span class="font-medium italic"> engineering</span>
      </h2>

      {/* Body */}
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-lg text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground md:text-lg">
        I'm drawn to the space where interfaces become craft — where motion, 
        interaction, and code converge into something that feels inevitable. 
        Not just usable, but alive.
      </p>

      {/* Signal */}
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-6">
        <span class="h-px w-12 bg-border/60" />
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider text-muted-foreground/60">
          Open to collaborations & experiments
        </span>
        <span class="h-px w-12 bg-border/60" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
